nitive account of the action=E2=80=94the young buyers injecting enthusiasm =
into the market; notes on the quality and sales of work this year; a breakd=
own of the flood of new V.I.P. fairgoers=E2=80=94which I=E2=80=99m excited =
to share with you. I did, however, have the distinct pleasure of attending =
<b>Andrew Ross Sorkin</b>=E2=80=99s DealBook conference last week, and my e=
ars perked up at something <b>Sam Altman</b>, OpenAI=E2=80=99s
