ly 5.5 percent more for a painting the=
y acquired with an irrevocable bid, the market for high-value works must be=
 pretty tough. <br/><br/>A last-minute snafu prevented me from getting on a=
 plane to Miami on Tuesday morning, but this hiccup gave me the benefit of =
having time to talk to a slew of dealers, collectors, and advisors to get a=
