wMjZ1dG1fc291cmNlPWN1c3RvbWVyLmlvXHUwMDI2dXRtX3Rlcm09ZjZjNjA2MTdkYTQyYWJkMT=
JhIiwiaW50ZXJuYWwiOiJmNmM2MDYxN2RhNDJhYmQxMmEiLCJsaW5rX2lkIjoyMDA2MTA5fQ/f9=
545939e0e667e48831d69cf54540d1a9b67d5d4c2c6a98e2c8fd8a77820895" style=3D"co=
lor:#d40000;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold" class=3D"sdf">about</a><=
/u> on Tuesday, he said the museum had a solid crowd, including a number of=
 out-of-town board
members, all supporting the shows enthusiastically. <br/><br/>From the ICA,=
 it=E2=80=99s a short ride or a decent walk to the Rubell Museum, where Ban=
k of America held its annual party. One of the real hazards of Art Week is =
navigating Miami=E2=80=99s brutal traffic. I got texts from friends making =
the trip from Miami Beach to the party in Allapattah who were trapped in Ub=
ers for up to two hours. Even with the traffic, my friend <b>Vincent Thomps=
on</b>, a private banker at BofA, said the event seemed =E2=80=9Cmore effer=
vescent this year=E2=80=9D and that the venue was noticeably fuller, which =
is saying something because I recall that the party was pretty packed last =
year. <br/><br/>The <b>Rubells</b> put on a show of new works and art by th=
eir artist in residence, <b>Vanessa Raw</b>, but the draw is always the dep=
th and audacity of their collecting. One of the first rooms off the central=
, upwardly sloping hallway=E2=80=94 which is filled with the 700 stainless =
steel spheres that constitute <b>Yayoi
Kusama</b>=E2=80=99s 1966 work <i>Narcissus Garden</i>=E2=80=94<u><a href=
=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0d=
